snippet.title: Sky Taxi 3: The Movie
snippet.description:
http://www.game-remakes.com/game.php?id=2008
Run, jump and double jump your way through dozens of side-scrolling levels, stomping on enemies and collecting goodies as you work through this Action and Arcade game. Find powerups that give your abilities a boost, battle Super Bosses, and locate secrets rooms and levels to pump up your score. Your mission: Catch Mr. Big Man, the world's most notorious gangster, before his minions takes over the world in Sky Taxi 3: The Movie!
